<div class="language- line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="" style="--shiki-light:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee;--shiki-light-bg:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code" v-pre=""><code class="language-"><span class="line"><span>https://www.bilibili.uno/api?server=:server&#x26;type=:type&#x26;id=:id&#x26;auth=:auth&#x26;r=:r</span></span></code></pre>
